---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Foundations — How to Use Psychedelics"
  description="Before setting an intention, ingesting a substance, visiting a clinic, or attending a ceremony, some foundational questions deserve attention: culture, law, science, and nature."
  canonicalPath="/foundations"
  hideProgress={true}
>

  <div class="content-page">

    <!-- Content Hero -->
    <div class="content-hero">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
      <span>Foundations</span>
    </div>
      <h1 class="content-hero-title">Foundations</h1>
      <p class="content-hero-subtitle">Before setting an intention, ingesting a substance, visiting a clinic, or attending a ceremony, some foundational questions deserve attention: <em>What do we know scientifically? What is the legal landscape? How did we get here culturally? And what is the relationship between psychedelics and the living world?</em></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Foundations Card Grid -->
    <div class="hub-grid">
      <a href="/culture" class="hub-card">
        <div class="card-num">01</div>
        <h3>Culture</h3>
        <p>History of psychedelic use across human cultures — from ancient ceremony to the modern renaissance and its tensions.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/law" class="hub-card">
        <div class="card-num">02</div>
        <h3>Law</h3>
        <p>Legal status by substance and jurisdiction, and what decriminalisation and legalisation actually mean in practice.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/science" class="hub-card">
        <div class="card-num">03</div>
        <h3>Science</h3>
        <p>How psychedelics work, what the evidence shows, and how to read the research critically without overstating preliminary findings.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/nature" class="hub-card">
        <div class="card-num">04</div>
        <h3>Nature</h3>
        <p>Why ecological themes arise so consistently in psychedelic experience — and what the research and the Psygaia framework say about it.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">Read &rarr;</div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Support Banner -->
    <div class="footer-support">
      <div class="footer-support-inner">
        <div class="footer-support-text">
          <p class="footer-support-label">Support Psychedelic Research &amp; Education</p>
          <p class="footer-support-headline">This work exists because people like you care.</p>
          <p class="footer-support-body">Psygaia is an independent nonprofit — no ads, no corporate sponsors. Just rigorous, freely available education in service of safer psychedelic practice and planetary health. Your support keeps this work alive.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="footer-support-btn" href="https://buy.stripe.com/bIYcMX3W893Z4o04gg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Support This Work →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>
